ADDITIONAL LOGISTICS & TRANSPORTATION DISCLAIMER

This software is provided as a technical demonstration of conversational AI
patterns for logistics and transportation services. It is NOT:

  • A licensed freight forwarder, courier, or carrier
  • A customs broker or licensed dangerous-goods (DG) handler
  • A real shipment-tracking or fleet-management system
  • A substitute for professional logistics, customs, or compliance advice

The included data (shipments, tracking numbers, fleet vehicles, warehouses,
routes, rates, customs figures) is entirely fictional. Names of carriers,
hubs, client companies, and locations are invented for demonstration
purposes. Tracking numbers do not correspond to any real shipment.

The shipment-screening logic (prohibited goods, dangerous goods, customs
misdeclaration detection) is a best-effort demonstration and is NOT a
substitute for proper regulatory compliance. Shipping dangerous or
prohibited goods is governed by national and international law (IATA DGR,
IMDG Code, national customs and transport regulations). Always consult a
certified dangerous-goods specialist and the relevant authorities.

Do not deploy this software to handle real shipments, real customer data,
real fleet operations, or real customs declarations without substantial
modification, professional audit, and compliance with all applicable
regulations.
